Class Project

Object
Project
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISearchable
public class Project extends Object implements ISearchable
Represents a Build-To-Order (BTO) housing project. Each project has a name, neighborhood, application window, visibility status, flat type breakdown, and assigned manager/officers. Implements ISearchable to support dynamic filtering for applicants and managers. Officer registration is limited by a maximum slot quota, and flat types are customizable.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Javier
